definitions.definition: A person who subscribes to a publication or a service .
examples: Our magazine has over ten thousand subscribers .

definitions.definition: A system or component that subscribes to something, such as an event , made available by a publisher .

main_definition: A person who subscribes to a publication or a service .
secondary_definitions: ( programming ) A system or component that subscribes to something, such as an event , made available by a publisher .
